title: Happy Birthday Amy! + Morgan2 Gives Her Side Of The Story On Going Out To A Bar This Weekend + Raymundo Has Been Texting Random Listeners
itunes:title: Happy Birthday Amy! + Morgan2 Gives Her Side Of The Story On Going Out To A Bar This Weekend + Raymundo Has Been Texting Random Listeners
description:
We celebrate Amy’s 39th birthday! We also talked to Morgan2 on the phone today. She gave her side of the story on having to stay home from work after going to a bar this weekend. Plus, a listener called in claiming Raymundo has been texting him about stock inquiries!
